
https://www.quora.com/What-is-the-ELK-stack

Log Management Platform

ELK = Elasticsearch + Logstash + Kibana

Elasticsearch = Non relational Database

Logstash = Log collection and transport the logs to Elasticsearch and save those.

Kibana = GUI and searching of logs from elasticsearch.


ELK is used for log searching and managing.

It's workflow  : Logstash to Elasticsearch to Kibana.
